    <description>Hello, 
Which GMless (/full, let&#39;s not play on words) TTRPGs do you know that reveal tiles or cards for exploration ? 
I have designed such a game for planet exploration and I want to learn the state of the art. 

I&#39;ve found only two games using cards as tiles so far : 
[Le voyageur immobile du palais de marbre](https://cendrones.itch.io/voyageur ) by Cendrones 
and a dungeon card game I forgot the name of which, which included solo RP.</description>
    
